snippet.title: Spellbound Spire - Official Teaser
snippet.description:
Spellbound Spire is being released on Steam June 23th!
We are participating in the Steam Games Festival. From June 16th till June 22th you can play our demo, listen to our broadcast,  and chat with us!

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1248270/Spellbound_Spire/

Follow us on social media:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SpellboundSpire
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/spellbound_spire
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SpellboundSpire

Spellbound Spire is a student game created by 3rd-year students at Breda University. It is made over the course of 28 weeks.

For business inquiries contact us at business@spellboundspire.nl
